    "analysis": "Across all revenue segments, the most common AI uses are **content creation for web/social media** and **product descriptions**, consistently ranking at the top regardless of business size. Merchants with revenues **up to 40,000 euros** most frequently use AI for text creation (19 traders) and photo editing (15), while those in the **200,000–500,000 euro** range prioritize product descriptions most (17 traders). Higher-revenue merchants (500,000–1,000,000 euros) show a more balanced distribution across fewer use cases, suggesting more focused and strategic AI adoption. Naprednije primjene poput **CRM sustava, AI chatbotova i dorađivanja webshopa** ostaju marginalne u svim segmentima prometa, s tek 1–3 trgovca po kategoriji."
